).', '1â€“3 g bark (KAP); 3.88 g powdered bark (PH2); 1 g dry bark/day or 2â€“6\r\nml extract (1:2) (KEB); 14â€“28 ml decoction (KAP).', 'Not covered (AHP; KOM). â€œHealth\r\nhazards not known with proper therapeutic dosagesâ€ (PH2). One case of acute myocardial infarction\r\ntentatively associated with use of arjuna (KEB).', 52, '', ''),
